title.narrative: HIV Vaccine and Biomedical Prevention Research Project: AVAC CASPR (Coalition to Accelerate and Support Prevention Research)

description.narrative: The Coalition to Accelerate and Support Prevention Research (CASPR) is designed to address this challenge through a robust network of strategic partnerships and an interconnected array of activities, all oriented towards the support, strengthening and impact of Africa-focused and Africa-led biomedical HIV prevention research, implementation and advocacy. The ultimate goal of this project is to support the development and sustainability of an African-centered network dedicated to advancing advocacy, policy, regulatory, community engagement and communication efforts that help accelerate biomedical HIV prevention research.
